    <stitle>SINGLE REDUCTION, TANDEM AXLES: SPICER J400-S, W460-S - REMOVE - INTER-AXLE DIFFERENTIAL</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="5">
        <title>INTER-AXLE DIFFERENTIAL</title>
        <para>Refer to
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1400408">Figure 8</hotlnk>.
        </para>
        <figure id="f1400408" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1400408" filename="../figg14/G1400408.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 8. Inter-Axle Differential Exploded View</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the inter-axle shift cylinder assembly, compress spring and remove retainer clip.
                Remove spring (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1400409">Figure 9</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1400409" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1400409" filename="../figg14/G1400409.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 9. Compress Spring and Remove Retainer Clip</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Screw shift fork shaft out of shift fork and remove shift fork shaft from differential
                carrier (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1400410">Figure 10</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1400410" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1400410" filename="../figg14/G1400410.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 10. Remove Shift Fork Shaft</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove inter-axle differential cover bolts (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1400411">Figure 11</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1400411" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1400411" filename="../figg14/G1400411.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 11. Remove Inter-Axle Differential Cover Bolts</caption>
            </figure>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>One bolt is slightly longer than the others and must be replaced in same position.</para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Lift inter-axle differential assembly from power divider intermediate case. Use of a hoist
                or overhead crane is recommended (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1400412">Figure 12</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1400412" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1400412" filename="../figg14/G1400412.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 12. Lift Inter-Axle Differential Assembly From Power Divider Intermediate Case</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
